cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI 

This paper is about co-saliency detection, which is a subfield of computer vision. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category. The paper also discusses feature extraction, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.MM - Multimedia), and potential applications of co-saliency detection, which could include information retrieval (cs.IR - Information Retrieval) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI - Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper discusses open issues and challenges, which could fall under the category of machine learning (cs.LG - Machine Learning).
